description:
This data set includes details of wild boar visits at the carcass sites based on the evaluation of pictures (Excel sheet 1 “Visits”; Excel sheet 2 “Visits summary”). It also includes pictures displaying the typical behavior of wild boar at the carcass sites.
Overview:
Supporting data Table 1 - Details pictures;
ESM Figure 1 - Wild boar rooting at site 3;
ESM Figure 2 - Wild boar are curious, but do not touch;
ESM Figure 3 - Wild boar attracted by the soft ground;
ESM Figure 4 - Wild boar chewing on bone;
ESM Figure 5 - Wild boar rolling on soft ground on site 3;
ESM Figure 6 - Ground underneath carcass 3 is stirred up;
ESM Figure 7 - Wild boar feeding on wild ruminant;
ESM Figure 8 - Skeletonization process of carcass 1;
